'''非洲臀果木'''（学名：''Prunus africana''）是[[蔷薇科|蔷薇科]][[李属|李属]][[常绿|常绿]][[乔木|乔木]]，原生於[[撒哈拉以南非洲|撒哈拉以南非洲]]的山區，以及[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]、[[聖多美|聖多美]]、[[比奧科|比奧科]]和[[大葛摩|大葛摩]]等島上高約900至3400公尺的地方。成熟的樹種在森林中高約10至25公尺、呈張開的枝條狀且通常是下垂的；在草地上則較短，且有10至20公尺寬的圓頂。非洲臀果木生長需要潮濕的氣候、900至3400公釐的降雨量且極度耐霜。<ref name=prunafr>{{cite web | title=Prunus africana (Hook. f.) Kalkman | work=Germplasm Resources Information Network (GRIN) Taxonomy for Plants | author=U. S. Department of Agriculture (USDA) | url=http://www.ars-grin.gov/cgi-bin/npgs/html/taxon.pl?29828 | format=html | accessdate=2008-03-14 | archive-date=2012-10-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010010948/http://www.ars-grin.gov/cgi-bin/npgs/html/taxon.pl?29828 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=pygafr>{{cite web | title=Pygeum africanum Hook. f. | work=Germplasm Resources Information Network (GRIN) Taxonomy for Plants | author=U. S. Department of Agriculture (USDA) | url=http://www.ars-grin.gov/cgi-bin/npgs/html/taxon.pl?30392 | format=html | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010011001/http://www.ars-grin.gov/cgi-bin/npgs/html/taxon.pl?30392 | archivedate=2012-10-10 }} </ref><ref>{{cite book | first=Najma | last=Dharani | title=Field Guide to Common Trees and Shrubs of East Africa | publisher=New Holland | date=2002 | isbn= 1-86872-640-1 | pages=page 150}} Previewable Google Books. </ref><ref name=sustain>{{cite web | last=Cunningham | first=A.B. | coauthors=Mbenkum, F.T. | title=Sustainability of harvesting Prunus africana bark in Cameroon: A medicinal plant in international trade | work=People and Plants working papers | publisher=Division of Ecological Sciences, UNESCO | date=May 1993 | url=http://peopleandplants.org/whatweproduce/Workingpapers/pdf/wp2.pdf | format=pdf | access-date=2008-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928100401/http://peopleandplants.org/whatweproduce/Workingpapers/pdf/wp2.pdf | archive-date=2007-09-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=who>{{ cite book | author=World Health Organization, Inc. NetLibrary | title=WHO Monographs on Selected Medicinal Plants: Volume 2 | publisher=World Health Organization | date=2002 | location=Geneva | isbn= 92-4-154537-2 | pages=page 246 }} Previewable Google Books.</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Nonjinge | first=Siyabulela | title=Prunus africana (Hook. f.) Kalkman | work=PlantZAfrica.com | publisher=South African National Biodiversity Institute | date=October 2006 | url=http://www.plantzafrica.com/plantnop/prunusafri.htm | format=html }}</ref>

